<subSubSection pageId="93" pageNumber="2323" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="93.[160,1155,558,722]" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,282,558,583]" italics="true" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
separated from other in the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Felsche" authorityYear="1901" box="[622,762,559,583]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Pinotus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadraticeps">
<emphasis box="[622,762,559,583]" italics="true" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323">quadraticeps</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group by the following combined characters: clypeo-genal angulation in larger males acute and forming a teeth (like 
<emphasis box="[160,556,628,652]" italics="true" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Nunes &amp; Vaz-de-Mello" authorityYear="2019" box="[160,297,628,652]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Dichotomius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="edmondsi">D. edmondsi</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Nunes &amp; Vaz-de-Mello" authorityYear="2019" box="[309,444,628,652]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Dichotomius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paschoali">D. paschoali</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Harold" authorityYear="1869" box="[456,556,628,652]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Pinotus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="reichei">D. reichei</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
); males pronotal disc with a central knob on anterior portion (idem); males cephalic horn or tubercle rounded apically and paramera in dorsal and ventral view strongly narrowed medially (as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Nunes &amp; Vaz-de-Mello" authorityYear="2019" box="[710,843,698,722]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Dichotomius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paschoali">
<emphasis box="[710,843,698,722]" italics="true" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323">D. paschoali</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Nunes &amp; Vaz-de-Mello" authorityYear="2019" box="[901,1025,698,722]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Dichotomius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="frizzasae">
<emphasis box="[901,1025,698,722]" italics="true" pageId="93" pageNumber="2323">D. frizzasae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
